{"tid":2133351,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實美國總統並無權自行改變選舉日期","createTime":"2020-07-31T04:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T06:23:23.000Z","uid":78519,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f91c15fc054c9add6869be89f734ee023362665","tid":2133351,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://medium.com/gausee-寰雨膠事錄/其實美國總統並無權自行改變選舉日期-a5126681ca9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fgausee-%E5%AF%B0%E9%9B%A8%E8%86%A0%E4%BA%8B%E9%8C%84%2F%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%A6%E7%84%A1%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F-a5126681ca9&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG11tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=99a2d57c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/gausee-寰雨膠事錄/其實美國總統並無權自行改變選舉日期-a5126681ca9</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統傳布週四推出震撼彈，其實是個問題，問可不可以將美國大選延期。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1288818160389558273?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1288818160389558273%3Fs%3D21&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG11tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=26b4d15f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1288818160389558273%3Fs%3D21&h=d438a0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1288818160389558273?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n推文一出，其實很多美國媒體很不在意，反而是英國媒體很在意，甚至推送，反而因此令一些美國媒體心虛，反過來推送。<br />\n<br />\n但熟書的美國媒體很快解話，美國總統選舉普選投票的日期，其實是法律已經定明，是11月1日之後第一個星期二。除非國會通過議案，否則是不可能改的。<br />\n<br />\n因此可以說總統無權，而且甚至傳出共和黨的參議院，也沒興趣做。自己黨控制的一院也無法推展，自然無法推到去民主黨控制的眾議院。<br />\n<br />\n而到美國時間周四下午，川普也推出一個 #我的貼文發生作用 的推文，表示自己是為了發起對郵寄選票的質疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1288932940337090561?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1288932940337090561%3Fs%3D21&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG11tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=afabc6e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1288932940337090561%3Fs%3D21&h=0ef09f4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1288932940337090561?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n至於大家信不信服這個理由，我們倒也覺得不所謂，今天潑到川普身上的髒水夠多的了。"},{"pid":"8384805833d9d8c78d7b4ceb7bd93506ee2456f5","tid":2133351,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7076bfd891fd7540381261f6bf39e48fe047b3bd","tid":2133351,"uid":134119,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"推乜鳩，呢條撚樣都痴痴地，香港人但行文成個台灣佬咁。戇撚柒鳩，用撚埋啲台灣腔唔撚代表你寫野文雅啲！九唔撚搭八！"},{"pid":"e588a4dc37c9f8ba3e596dc3041123f39d26c924","tid":2133351,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e4f456b3add321e892674702de5b5b34e3960e8","tid":2133351,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7076bfd891fd7540381261f6bf39e48fe047b3bd","tid":2133351,"uid":134119,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"推乜鳩，呢條撚樣都痴痴地，香港人但行文成個台灣佬咁。戇撚柒鳩，用撚埋啲台灣腔唔撚代表你寫野文雅啲！九唔撚搭八！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc76bced9b4bb4e2a42ebe9709b422add28634c","tid":2133351,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb15b79ab77101a5c6522202823050723bf30318","tid":2133351,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"試吓講retweet，唔好講推送"},{"pid":"1b31eb4fe1c84a6c1cdadb1fb5d48921b94aecef","tid":2133351,"uid":78519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb15b79ab77101a5c6522202823050723bf30318","tid":2133351,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc